ght...  Lets say I kill the chief, loot his head, can I immediately just walk over to garadain, wherever he is (on top of the ridge or wherever) and hand him the head or do I gotta wait for him to charge in? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ucoray.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Coray</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/16/01 1:10:14 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question on 8th ring war - piece of cake</span><hr size=1> Wait for Garadain to shout charge before turning it in.  He takes a bit to do that, the troops organize out a ways from the fort then move up to the ridge just in front, soon after he yells charge and you can hand it in for your ring. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usplaktar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Splaktar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_greenspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/19/01 12:19:45 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question on 8th ring war - piece of cake</span><hr size=1> Yeah, it's gotta be after he yells charge.<br>
I turned it in last week before he yelled charge and it just poofed.<br>
<br>
Then I tried a 2nd time and let him go into the fort.  We were killing everything<br>
and Garadain was hitting them too, but was at 80% health because I was tanking.<br>
Then we killed the last things and all the sudden he takes off running... into<br>
the fort wall and poofs...<br>
<br>
So I'm still waiting around for 3rd Gloradain... ugh <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uprodigious.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Prodigious</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/19/01 5:00:00 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question on 8th ring war - piece of cake</span><hr size=1> ok here's how it goes:<br>
<br>
hand in ring to garadain, get note<br>
<br>
hand in note to gloradin. she repops or something. the 2 giants and 3 orcs spawn inside the fort (where your friends should be, a bit away from the gate. now run back invis to them, pull the chief with a lvl 60 (easy to get single), kill him and loot head.<br>
<br>
now all giants and orcs outside the fort should have spawned as well.<br>
<br>
invis out past the gates and wait in front of the gates approx at the tree where people usually fight. after a few minutes, a lot of dorfs will spawn over the hill and get ready. Garadain will kinda warp onto that hill just as he shouts charge, and the dorfs will run in to fight the giants/orcs.<br>
<br>
garadain now walks in a straigh patch towards and through the gate. hand him the Chief's head AFTER he shouts charge, and as soon as possible after he does so.<br>
<br>
the dorfs should win the war and kill all giants/orcs (was a clean fight when I did mine), and garadain is supposed to be able to walk untouched through the gates while the other dorfs fight. but you never know, so hand him the head right after he shouts charge and you should be fine. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uxaem.showPublicProfile?language=EN>xaem</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/19/01 8:10:27 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Got 8th ring</span><hr size=1> Got my 8th ring, thx guys, I waited from 8 am to midnight for gloradin to spawn, was well worth it hehe <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=3315.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=3308.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=3287.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadControl?topicID=3287.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3287.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3287.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br